Title: Father Dad
Director: Luana Claxton Fredericks, Shaan Davis, Jason Harry, Kenya Cagle, Sherman Jones
Actors: Leila Velez, Natalie Belus, Kenyae Cagle, Luana Claxton
Plot: Father Dad is about a man who marries a woman with children from a previous relationship. After ten years, the biological father returns and decides that he is going to take his family back...
